-- Zhongwang Borrows 2.3 Billion Yuan, Lends It to Builder, Newspaper Reports
-- Stanley James
-- 2010-04-21T22:31:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-21/zhongwang-borrows-2-3-billion-yuan-lends-it-to-builder-newspaper-reports.html

          
          
             China Zhongwang Holdings Ltd. 
borrowed 2.3 billion yuan from banks and lent the money to a 
construction company owned by the Liaoning provincial 
government, the South China Morning Post reported, citing 
Zhongwang’s annual report.  
 Zhongwang said it isn’t responsible for repaying the loan 
to the Liaoning banks, according to the Morning Post.    
          
          


  


        